1.) Create a react app by running:

npx create-react-app <project name>

our example is npx create-react-app frontend

2.) In the terminal:
  cd frontend
  
3.) In the terminal:
  npm start
  
4.) Next we will add React bootstrap framework in the terminal with:
  npm install react-bootstrap bootstrap

5.) Next install react-router-dom 5.2.0 in the terminal with:
  npm install --save react-router-dom@5.2.0
  
6. Add the following code to App.js:
  import React from 'react'
import { Switch, Route, Link } from "react-router-dom"
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
  
7.) Test by running in the terminal:
  npm start

NEXT WE WILL CREATE THE NAVIGATION HEADER BAR
